channel.title: Need Help From 317 PI Server Owners! VERY VERY SIMPLE FOR YOU!
channel.description: I know I may sound noob and retarded... But I need help from somebody who owns a 317 PI to set mine up. I have a source (untouched by me) and have no clue on setting it up, due to the fact that I'm new to Project Insanity. I have always used Delta but from what I see PI is the better way to go. Could somebody please Teamviewer with me to help me set it up, so I'll know how to in the future. I'm not used to the bin and src files and stuff. Could somebody please help and explain? I'll easily REP++ for any help at all. :) Thanks!!
